uploadedTagObject = system.util.jsonDecode(value)
	#sorted(data, key=lambda x: x["age"])
	tags = uploadedTagObject["tags"]
	tagsSorted = sorted(tags, key=lambda tag: tag["name"])
	
	sortedTagObject = {}
	
	def sortTagObject(tagObject):
	
		if "tags" in tagObject:
			sortedTags = sorted(tagObject["tags"], key=lambda tag: tag["name"])
			tagObject["tags"] = sortedTags
			for innerTagObject in tagObject["tags"]:
				innerTagObject = sortTagObject(innerTagObject) 
				
			
		return tagObject
		
	sortedTagObject = sortTagObject(uploadedTagObject)
			
	return sortedTagObject
